{"ja476:0.1":"Jataka ","ja476:0.2":"Terasakanipata ","ja476:0.3":"Ambavagga ","ja476:0.4":"3. Javanahamsajataka ","ja476:1.1":"“Idheva hamsa nipata, ","ja476:1.2":"piyam me tava dassanam; ","ja476:1.3":"Issarosi anuppatto, ","ja476:1.4":"yamidhatthi pavedaya”. ","ja476:2.1":"“Savanena ekassa piya bhavanti, ","ja476:2.2":"Disva panekassa viyeti chando; ","ja476:2.3":"Disva ca sutva ca piya bhavanti, ","ja476:2.4":"Kaccinnu me piyasi dassanena. ","ja476:3.1":"Savanena piyo mesi, ","ja476:3.2":"bhiyyo cagamma dassanam; ","ja476:3.3":"Evam piyadassano me, ","ja476:3.4":"vasa hamsa mamantike”. ","ja476:4.1":"“Vaseyyama tavagare, ","ja476:4.2":"niccam sakkatapujita; ","ja476:4.3":"Matto ca ekada vajje, ","ja476:4.4":"‘hamsarajam pacantu me’”. ","ja476:5.1":"“Dhiratthu tam majjapanam, ","ja476:5.2":"yam me piyataram taya; ","ja476:5.3":"Na capi majjam pissami, ","ja476:5.4":"yava me vacchasi ghare”. ","ja476:6.1":"“Suvijanam singalanam, ","ja476:6.2":"sakunananca vassitam; ","ja476:6.3":"Manussavassitam raja, ","ja476:6.4":"dubbijanataram tato. ","ja476:7.1":"Api ce mannati poso, ","ja476:7.2":"nati mitto sakhati va; ","ja476:7.3":"Yo pubbe sumano hutva, ","ja476:7.4":"paccha sampajjate diso. ","ja476:8.1":"Yasmim mano nivisati, ","ja476:8.2":"avidure sahapi so; ","ja476:8.3":"Santikepi hi so dure, ","ja476:8.4":"yasmim navisate mano. ","ja476:9.1":"Antopi so hoti pasannacitto, ","ja476:9.2":"Param samuddassa pasannacitto; ","ja476:9.3":"Antopi so hoti padutthacitto, ","ja476:9.4":"Param samuddassa padutthacitto. ","ja476:10.1":"Samvasanta vivasanti, ","ja476:10.2":"ye disa te rathesabha; ","ja476:10.3":"Ara santo samvasanti, ","ja476:10.4":"manasa ratthavaddhana. ","ja476:11.1":"Aticiram nivasena, ","ja476:11.2":"piyo bhavati appiyo; ","ja476:11.3":"Amanta kho tam gacchama, ","ja476:11.4":"pura te homa appiya”. ","ja476:12.1":"“Evance yacamananam, ","ja476:12.2":"Anjalim navabujjhasi; ","ja476:12.3":"Paricarakanam satam, ","ja476:12.4":"Vacanam na karosi no; ","ja476:12.5":"Evam tam abhiyacama, ","ja476:12.6":"Puna kayirasi pariyayam”. ","ja476:13.1":"“Evance no viharatam, ","ja476:13.2":"antarayo na hessati; ","ja476:13.3":"Tuyhancapi maharaja, ","ja476:13.4":"mayhanca ratthavaddhana; ","ja476:13.5":"Appeva nama passemu, ","ja476:13.6":"ahorattanamaccaye”ti. ","ja476:14.1":"Javanahamsajatakam tatiyam. "}